com.credenceid.biometrics

Interface Biometrics.OnMRZReaderListener

  • Enclosing interface:
    Biometrics

    public static interface Biometrics.OnMRZReaderListener
    Interface definition for a callbacks to be invoked when a request to Biometrics.readMRZ(OnMRZReaderListener) returns with results.

    • Method Detail

      • onMRZRead

        void onMRZRead(Biometrics.ResultCode resultCode,
               java.lang.String hint,
               byte[] rawData,
               java.lang.String rawString,
               java.lang.String parsedString)
        Invoked when a request to Biometrics.readMRZ(OnMRZReaderListener) returns with results.
        Parameters:
        resultCode - Biometrics.ResultCode.OK if MRZ was successfully read. Biometrics.ResultCode.FAIL} if MZ failed to be read. Biometrics.ResultCode.INTERMEDIATE} may be returned while operation is still ongoing.
        hint - Textual representation of what is going on with operation
        rawData - Raw data from MRZ in Byte array format.
        rawString - Raw data from MRZ in string format
        parsedString - If resultCode is Biometrics.ResultCode.OK then this string will contain ten items, each separated by a newline character. If this string is split, it SHOULD contain TEN items.

        DOB String Date of Birth, usually in the form YYMMDD Expiry String Expiry date of document (usually YYMMDD Issuer String 3 character country code of document issuer Document Type String 1 or 2 character document type Last Name String Last name First Name String First name(s) may be truncated Nationality String 3 character country code of document holder Discretionary String Supplementary data on document Discretionary2 String Supplementary data on document Document Number String Unique document identifier Sex char Gender (M/F/X)
